rubrics, used to evaluate the studies, can be found in Ivarsson
and Gorschek [51]. To obtain the study‚Äôs Ô¨Ånal score, we sum the
individual scores of the rigor and relevance aspects.

In order to rank the papers,we deÔ¨Åned a function incorporating
the classiÔ¨Åcation schema, rigor and relevance scores, and two addi
