contribution needs however to be qualiÔ¨Åed by the reader [51].

The validity of the ranking function (see Section 3.6) is threa
tened by the arbitrarily chosen scores for each category and
weights for each dimension. To mitigate this threat, we used an
automatic spreadsheet to compute the Ô¨Ånal scores, allowing us
to adjust scores and weights, observing the effect of the Ô¨Ånal rank
